dcterms:description: A synthetic dataset generated by filtering out duplicates and empty images in combinations of shape and operation actions in text. The dataset includes images constructed from geometric shapes, with a search space for an image up to 3 shapes (or program length 5) being around 1.8×10^5.
dcterms:title: Synthetic 2D CSG Dataset

dcterms:description: A 2D CAD dataset containing binary 64 × 64 images of various furniture items. The dataset is used to evaluate the performance of the proposed algorithm in approximating CAD images with programs.
dcterms:title: 2D CAD Furniture Dataset
